## Project Overview

> This repository presents my complete solution to the **ELTA Data Analyst Home Task**,  
> demonstrating strong analytical thinking, structured problem-solving, and the ability  
> to extract meaningful business insights from raw data.

Throughout this project I showcase the **full analytical lifecycle** — from raw data to **actionable conclusions**.

---

## What’s Inside?

###  Data Exploration & Cleaning
- Understanding the dataset structure  
- Handling missing values  
- Fixing inconsistencies and preparing clean, reliable data

###  Feature Engineering
- Creating new meaningful features  
- Enhancing analytical depth and business relevance

###  Analytical Reasoning
- Identifying trends, patterns, and anomalies  
- Applying statistical thinking for accurate conclusions

### Business Insights
- Translating numbers into clear business stories  
- Producing insights that support real decision-making

